description.value: There is only one corner of the universe you can be certain of improving, and that's your own self...
Think in the morning. Act in the noon. Eat in the evening. Sleep in the night......
Love cures people - both the ones who give it and the ones who receive it...
Keep your face always toward the sunshine - and shadows will fall behind you...

excerpt.value: mixcore is a free, open source, community-focused Content Management System (CMS) built on the ASP.NET Core | Dotnet Core platform software you can use to create a beautiful website, blog, forum, or app.

body.value:
Mixcore CMS

Tutorials

Demo: http://dev.mixcore.org

Docs: https://docs.mixcore.org

Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChqzh6JnC8HBUSQ9AWIcZAw

Twitter: https://twitter.com/mixcore_cms

GITs clone

mkdir mixcore

cd mixcore

git clone https://github.com/mixcore/mix.heart.git

git clone https://github.com/mixcore/mix.identity.git

git clone https://github.com/mixcore/mix.core.git
